{{Infobox Website |name = PsyArXiv |logo = PsyArXiv_logo.png |screenshot = |caption = |url = [http://www.psyarxiv.com psyarxiv.com] |alexa = |commercial = No |type = Science |language = English |registration = |owner = [[Society for the Improvement of Psychological Science]] |author = |launch date = {{start date and age|2016|09|}} |current status = Online |oclc = |issn = |revenue = }}
'''PsyArXiv''' is a preprint repository for the psychological sciences opened in September 2016<ref name=PsyArXiv_blog>{{cite web |date=19 September 2016 |title=Introducing PsyArXiv: a preprint service for psychological science |url=http://blog.psyarxiv.com/psyarxiv/2016/09/19/introducing-psyarxiv/ |work=PsyArXiv Blog|accessdate=2017-05-17}}</ref> and officially launched in December 2016.<ref name=PsyArXiv_blog2>{{cite web |date=8 December 2016 |title=Introducing PsyArXiv: Psychology's dedicated open access digital archive |url=http://blog.psyarxiv.com/psyarxiv/2016/12/08/psyarxiv-press-release/ |work=PsyArXiv Blog|accessdate=2017-05-17}}</ref><ref name=COS>{{cite web |date=5 December 2016 |title=The Center for Open Science Releases a Comprehensive, Open Source Preprints Solution |url=https://cos.io/about/news/center-open-science-releases-comprehensive-open-source-preprints-solution/ |work=[[Center for Open Science]]|accessdate=2017-05-17}}</ref> It is hosted by the [[Center for Open Science]].<ref>https://news.virginia.edu/content/psychology-professor-releases-free-open-source-preprint-software</ref> The preprint service was inspired by the [[arXiv]] repository. The service allows researchers to upload manuscripts regarding psychology and related fields prior to peer review.<ref>http://www.the-scientist.com/?articles.view/articleNo/48454/title/Funders-Back-Centralized-Bio-Preprint-Server/</ref> As of April 2017, it is indexed by Google Scholar.<ref name=Scholar>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/JeffSpies/status/853327239848632321|title=Jeffrey Spies on Twitter|work=Twitter|access-date=2017-05-17|language=en}}</ref>
==Fields== PsyArXiv accepts submissions in the following areas of research:<ref name=PsyArXiv_site>{{cite web |title=PsyArXiv |url=https://osf.io/preprints/psyarxiv |work=PsyArXiv|accessdate=2017-05-17}}</ref> {{columns-list|colwidth=30em| *[[Applied behavior analysis]] *[[Biological psychology]] *[[Child psychology]] *[[Clinical psychology]] *[[Cognition]] and [[perception]] *[[Cognitive psychology]] *[[Community psychology]] *[[Counseling psychology]] *[[Cultural psychology]] *[[Developmental psychology]] *Experimental analysis of behavior *[[Health psychology]] *[[Industrial and organizational psychology]] *[[Linguistics]] *[[Neuroscience]] and [[neurobiology]] *[[Operations research]], [[systems engineering]] and [[industrial engineering]] *[[Pain management]] *[[Personality]] and social contexts *[[Quantitative psychology]] *[[School psychology]] *[[Social psychology]] *Theory and philosophy }}
